{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8fa9b5908f","title":"关于将河南两派领导人调来北京商谈解决问题等的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2fd4959e34","index":0,"year":1967,"month":4,"day":23,"articleId":"8fa9b5908f","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"刘建勋","id":"3ae36abefb","type":"人物"},{"name":"干部和干部政策","id":"3df4ae75e1","type":"主题"},{"name":"林彪","id":"44b4a39710","type":"人物"},{"name":"军队和军事","id":"6f7a683373","type":"主题"},{"name":"文敏生","id":"9047f04de9","type":"人物"},{"name":"纪登奎","id":"9a50528209","type":"人物"},{"name":"批示","id":"9bc2c334c7","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"各级党政领导人","id":"a59dfa2519","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"e2305b9e63","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[{"id":"76e3f754f2","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"8fa9b5908f","publication":{},"article":{},"index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语是毛泽东看了中共河南省军区委员会1967年4月22日关于河南各造反派组织准备近日派4000余名代表进京反映问题的报告后写的。"},{"id":"36549a37c5","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"8fa9b5908f","publication":{},"article":{},"index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈再道，当时任中国人民解放军武汉军区司令员。钟汉华，当时任中国人民解放军武汉军区政治委员。刘建勋，当时任中国人民解放军河南省军区第一政委。"},{"id":"ce092b04f8","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"8fa9b5908f","publication":{},"article":{},"index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"赵文甫，当时任中共河南省委书记处书记、副省长。"},{"id":"980b616043","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"8fa9b5908f","publication":{},"article":{},"index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"文敏生，当时任中共河南省委代理第一书记、河南省省长。纪登奎、戴苏理，当时均任中共河南省委书记处候补书记。杨蔚屏，当时任中共河南省委书记处书记。"}],"contents":[{"id":"ddb2803e5d","type":"title","text":"关于将河南两派领导人调来北京商谈解决问题等的批语叫","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"8fa9b5908f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"76e3f754f2","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪、恩来同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"8fa9b5908f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"36549a37c5","type":"paragraph","text":"河南问题争得厉害，请商陈再道、钟汉华、刘建勋诸同志，是否将两派领导人调来谈一次，省军区只保一个赵文甫，将刘建勋、文敏生、纪登奎、戴苏理、杨蔚屏都不要，这种看法是否适当，值得研究。又湖北问题也很大，几乎省委天都是环人，也应快点研究为宜。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"8fa9b5908f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ce092b04f8","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"8fa9b5908f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"980b616043","type":"paragraph","text":"西月二十三日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"8fa9b5908f","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":420,"end":420}},"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"028574f6de","type":"paragraph","text":"河南问题争得厉害，请商陈再道、钟汉华、刘建勋诸同志，是否将两派领导人调来谈一次，省军区只保一个赵文甫，将刘建勋、文敏生、纪登奎、戴苏理、杨蔚屏都不要，这种看法是否适当，值得研究。又湖北问题也很大，几乎省委大都是坏人，也应快点研究为宜。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8fa9b5908f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"077f04b8b1","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪、恩来同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8fa9b5908f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"090bbe292a","type":"title","text":"关于将河南两派领导人调来北京商谈解决问题等的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8fa9b5908f","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}